      decisionTitle: 'Settings with the best balance',
      decision: ['Start with sensitive permissions: location, camera, microphone, contacts, notifications and background apps. Review app by app instead of cutting features you need.', 'Then review optional diagnostics, advertising ID, activity history and recommendations. On a shared computer, separate accounts protect more than one mixed profile.'],
      practiceTitle: 'Privacy maintenance',
      practice: ['Review permissions after installing new programs or major updates. Some apps request access for convenience, not necessity.', 'For work or children, combine privacy with security: screen lock, encryption, backups and a non-admin account. Reducing data does not compensate for an unprotected device.'],
      steps: ['Open Settings > Privacy & security.', 'Review location, camera and microphone.', 'Limit unnecessary background apps.', 'Adjust diagnostics and advertising ID.', 'Create separate accounts for different users.'],
