      context: ['A proxy forwards requests between your app and the destination. It can be used for filtering, caching, business control or changing the exit point of a specific app. It does not always encrypt traffic by itself.', 'A VPN usually creates an encrypted network interface that routes more device traffic to a server. Its scope is often wider, though configuration and exceptions matter.'],
