      decision: ['If you configure a proxy only in the browser, other apps may still use the normal connection. With a VPN, many apps use the tunnel, but leaks can exist if DNS, IPv6 or exceptions are poorly configured.', 'For privacy, the question is not just "proxy or VPN", but who operates it, what it logs, what it encrypts and which traffic remains outside.'],
